title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Aug 25 2021
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Aug 25 2021
description:
Johnny “Joey” Jones, (Ret.) U.S. Marine Corps bomb technician and Fox News contributor joins Clay and Buck to discuss what the Taliban’s red line deadline really means and why this matters to the homeland. New Trump ad "Surrenderer-In-Chief: Joe Biden lied to America and to the World". Officer who shot Ashli Babbitt to reveal identity in NBC News interview.
